  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 2 \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b93\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "2 trains will not run from the first day",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The train services from Nanu Oya to Colombo Fort and from Colombo Fort to Nanu Oya on daily routes 1023 and 1024 will be suspended from the 1st of next month.",
        "The train will leave Nanu Oya Railway Station at 6 am and reach Colombo Fort at 1.30 pm. The train will leave Colombo Fort Railway Station at 12.40 pm and reach Nanu Oya Railway Station at 9.30 pm.",
        "Most of the tourists on these trains go to Nuwara Eliya and in addition to these students including Patalai and government officials also benefit from these train services.",
        "However, steps have been taken to stop both the trains and resume delivery of goods with two compartments on time from the first of next month."
      ],
